To delete your game data, follow these steps:

- Open your device's Settings.
- Go to 'Apps' or 'Applications Manager'.
- Find and tap on 'Roboleap' from the list of installed apps.
- Tap on 'Storage & cache' or 'Storage'.
- Tap on 'Clear storage' or 'Clear data'.

Please note that clearing storage will delete all your progress and saved data in the game. If you're sure you want to proceed, confirm the action when prompted.
